quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  7,58,"And the good/pure country/land its plants appear/emerge with its Lord`s permission , and which became (was) bad/spoiled , does not appear/emerge except very little/useless/weak, as/like that We elaborate linguistically (explain in detail) the verses/evidences to a nation thinking/being grateful"
  7,59,"We had sent Noah to his nation, so he said: \"My nation worship God, (there) is not a God for you from other than Him, that I, I fear on (for) you a great day`s torture"
  7,60,"The nobles/assembly from his nation said: \"We , we are seeing you (E) in evident misguidance"
  7,61,"He said: \"My nation, (there) is not misguidance with me, and but I am a messenger from the creations all together`s/(universes`) Lord"
  7,62,"I communicate/deliver to you my Lord`s messages, and I advise to you, and I know from God what you do not now"
  7,63,"Are you astonished/surprised that a reminder came to you from your Lord on a man from you to warn/give you notice, and to fear and obey (E), and maybe/perhaps you attain mercy"
  7,64,"So they denied Him , so We saved/rescued him and those with him in the ship , and We drowned/sunk those who denied with Our verses/evidences , that they truly were a blind/confused/misguided nation"
  7,65,"And to Aad/an ancient tribe that could have been Hegaz, (We sent) their brother Hood, he said: \"My nation worship God, (there is) no God for you from other than Him, so do you not fear and obey"
  7,66,"The nobles/assembly , those who disbelieved from his nation said: \"That We , we (are) seeing/understanding you (E) in ignorance/stupidity , and (that) we suspect you (E) are from the disbelievers"
  7,67,"He said: \"My nation (there) is no ignorance/stupidity with me, and but I (am) a messenger from the creations all together`s/(universes`) Lord"